article:
The following '[[list of constellations]] in different languages' are the 88
designated constellations of the International Astronomical Union (IAU).
Constellations are presented in tabular form and link directly to the
corresponding non-English Wikipedia entry. The list of languages is not
complete, but gives examples from multiple language families for which entries
for all constellations are available. Languages are listed in alphabetical
order, with the exception of English and Latin.
